net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data

Class SimpleFilteredListModel<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.AbstractListModel
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.SimpleFilteredListModel<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type elements in the model.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilteredListModel<E>, ListModel

    public class SimpleFilteredListModel<E>
extends AbstractListModel
implements FilteredListModel<E>
    An implementation of FilteredListModel backed by a List object. This implementation internally maintains the original list but provides a filtered view of it.
    Author:
    Ben Barber (bbarber@i2rd.com)
